all teacher tasks under this package
Students should be able to:
- Manage student grades
    - Add initial grades
    - Update grades (for resits)
    - Calculate weighted mean grade (for particular student)
    - Determine student progression (I.e. register for next level, repeat level, graduate, fail)
    - Calculate degree result (degree class at the end of course)
- View student status
    - Showing grades for each period/level of study
    - Showing outcome for each level and eventually for whole degree